*
* Low-Pass Filter + Limiter
*

* forces current values to be saved
.options savecurrents

******************************************

*transformer
VIN tr1 0 0 sin(0 230 50 0 0)
RS tr1 tr2 10
L1 tr2 0 1155.555555
L2 A C 20
K L1 L2 0.99999

*full wave bridge rectifier
D1 A 1 Default
D2 C 1 Default
D3 0 A Default
D4 0 C Default

*Envelope detector
De 1 2 Default
Re 2 0 30k
Ce 2 0 30u

*voltage regulator
Rf 2 q 30k
Dp1 q 3 Default
